{"name": "odoo-addon-contract-sale-generation", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-contract-sale-generation", "version": "16.0.1.1.0.6", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/contract", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo-addon-contract-sale", "odoo"], "summary": "Contracts Management - Recurring Sales", "upload_time": 1716953786}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fcontract-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/contract\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/contract/tree/16.0/contract_sale_generation\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/contract-16-0/contract-16-0-contract_sale_generation\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/contract&target_branch=16.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Contracts Management - Recurring Sales\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:f86ca92372fb642d644f7a98d63c9db3ed81232c8ad02ef4afa66bddc64ec2f6\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module extends functionality of contracts to be able to generate sales\norders instead of invoices.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nTo use this module, you need to:\n\n1. Go to Sales -> Contracts and select or create a new contract.\n\n2. Fill fields for selecting the recurrency and invoice parameters:\n\n   - Type defines document that contract will generate, can be \"Sales\" or \"Invoices\"\n   - Sale Autoconfirm, validate Sales Orders if type is \"Sales\"\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/contract/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/contract/issues/new?body=module:%20contract_sale_generation%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- ACSONE SA/NV\n- PESOL\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Angel Moya \\<<mailto:angel.moya@pesol.es>>\n- Florent THOMAS \\<<mailto:florent.thomas@mind-and-go.com>>\n- Serpent Consulting Services Pvt. Ltd. \\<<mailto:support@serpentcs.com>>\n- Denis Roussel \\<<mailto:denis.roussel@acsone.eu>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/contract](https://github.com/OCA/contract/tree/16.0/contract_sale_generation) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.contract_sale_generation.models", "documentation": ["License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.contract_sale_generation.models.abstract_contract", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.contract_sale_generation.models..abstract_contract", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.contract_sale_generation.models.contract", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.contract_sale_generation.models..contract", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.contract_sale_generation.models.contract_line", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.contract_sale_generation.models..contract_line", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.contract_sale_generation.models.sale_order", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.contract_sale_generation.models..sale_order", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.contract_sale_generation.models.sale_order_line", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.contract_sale_generation.models..sale_order_line", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.contract_sale_generation.models.abstract_contract", "documentation": ["Copyright 2017 Pesol (<http://pesol.es>)", "Copyright 2017 Angel Moya <angel.moya@pesol.es>", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.contract_sale_generation.models.abstract_contract.ContractAbstractContract", "bases": ["models.AbstractModel"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.contract_sale_generation.models.abstract_contract.ContractAbstractContract._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.contract_sale_generation.models.abstract_contract.ContractAbstractContract.sale_autoconfirm", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.contract_sale_generation.models.